Subject: [PATCH 1/6] refactor: optimize backend, add frontend UI and tests

- Fix set_device_volume to filter only active render devices (was scanning all devices)
- Add batch volume endpoint (POST /api/volume/batch) to reduce HTTP calls during crossfade
- Add proper input validation on device_id (type check + length limit)
- Replace print statements with structured logging
- Optimize COM init with thread-local tracking (avoid repeated CoInitialize calls)
- Remove unused imports (CLSCTX_ALL, IAudioEndpointVolume)
- Create full radial mixer frontend with canvas-based UI, drag interaction,
  inverse-distance volume weighting, glow effects, and setup guide
- Add 17 unit tests covering all API routes and volume control logic
- Expand .gitignore for Python/IDE artifacts
- Remove placeholder hello-world test file

